textAnnotations.description:
Immersed in the Dinas Advertiser, was the
Rev. Eduards. Now he put down his paper,
folded it, and glanced idly out of the
window. Looked again, eyes starting from
his head. "God bless my immortal sol,"
he cried.
Never mind
"
yorar immortal
soud," said Mogan Thomas tartly.
Here we are
traversing the heavens at the
very moment when we should be
running into Llangril bus station.
